ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMERS:

Data Destruction Warning:
This software is designed to permanently and irreversibly destroy data.
Users assume full responsibility for data loss resulting from the use of
this software. Always verify target devices and backup important data
before using sanitization functions.

Security Compliance:
While this software is designed to meet industry standards including
NIST SP 800-88, users are responsible for validating compliance with
their specific security requirements and applicable regulations.

Administrator Privileges:
This software requires administrator privileges for low-level disk access.
Users should understand the security implications of running software
with elevated privileges.

Export Controls:
Cryptographic sanitization methods may be subject to export controls.
Users are responsible for compliance with applicable export regulations.

Professional Use:
For enterprise and government deployments, professional validation and
certification services are recommended to ensure compliance with specific
organizational security requirements.